ZH: 我下周要休假。
EN: I will take a vacation next week.

ZH: 这是我今年的最后一次休假。
EN: This is my last holiday this year.

ZH: 我正在考虑什么时候休假。
EN: I am considering when to take a vacation.

ZH: 我想在夏天休假去海边。
EN: I want to take a vacation to the beach in summer.

ZH: 他休假一星期去旅游。
EN: He took a one-week vacation to travel.

ZH: 我需要休假来照顾我的家人。
EN: I need a vacation to take care of my family.

ZH: 我正在休假，所以没法与你约会。
EN: I am on vacation, so I can't go on a date with you.

ZH: 我计划在明年的这个时候休长假。
EN: I plan to take a long vacation at this time next year.

ZH: 学校会在寒假期间休假。
EN: The school will take a vacation during the winter break.

ZH: 我最近感觉疲惫，需要休个长假。
EN: I feel exhausted lately and need a long vacation.

ZH: 我已经好几个月没休假了，需要休息一下。
EN: I haven't taken a vacation for several months and need some rest.

ZH: 我打算在休假期间读几本好书。
EN: I plan to read some good books during the vacation.

ZH: 我在休假时会尽量少使用手机。
EN: I will try to use my phone less during my vacation.

ZH: 我们公司每年会给员工发放带薪休假。
EN: Our company provides paid vacations for employees every year.

ZH: 这次休假我想学习一些新技能。
EN: During this vacation, I want to learn some new skills.

ZH: 我和我的家人一起去乡村休假。
EN: I went on vacation to the countryside with my family.

ZH: 我今天收到了批准休假的通知。
EN: I received a notice approving my vacation today.

ZH: 我已经预订了机票和酒店，准备休假了。
EN: I have already booked the flights and hotel, ready for my vacation.

ZH: 我的经理同意我提前休假。
EN: My manager agreed to let me take an early vacation.

ZH: 我下周要休假，所以我不能参加会议。
EN: I will take a vacation next week, so I won't be able to attend the meeting.
